pr_title: CATROID-1125 Add single-object to current scene
pr_body:
https://jira.catrob.at/browse/CATROID-1125
- implementation of the functionality
- possible conflicts: local and global variables with the same name
- conflict occurs: abort the import
- test cases for conflicting and nonconflicting imports

pr_title: CATROID-1210 wrong behaviour when importing objects from medialibrary
pr_body:
https://jira.catrob.at/browse/CATROID-1210

Because of the .catrobat extension of the downloaded project file, the project was not imported into the current project, but downloaded as a normal project and added to the project list.
